name 'networks-preassessment-intro_v2-2025'
title 'Networks and the Internet Pre-Assessment'
markdown <<MARKDOWN
This assessment will help measure your prior knowledge about how computer networks, the Internet, data transmission, security, and emerging technologies work.

- You are **not expected to know all the answers**! This is just to see what you already understand.
- Read each question carefully and **choose the best answer** based on what you know.
- There are **no penalties for incorrect answers**, so do your best!
MARKDOWN
